Business Brief -- Glenex Industries Inc.:
   Colorization Inc. Operations
   To Be Halted Due to Cost
Glenex has interests in oil and gas production, chemicals
and post-production graphics for videotape. Its loss for the
nine months ended Dec. 31 was C$3.4 million, or 38 Canadian
cents (32 U.S. cents) a share, on revenue of C$6 million.
   Glenex shares sank 12.5 U.S. cents each to 31.25 U.S.
cents in national over-the-counter trading yesterday.